Creating Left Two Main KPIs Per Day Per Port Entry and YoY Entry 11

Create Entries Per day KPI 

- Bring Card  from the visualization to the report pane > Select Per Day Per Port measure   As Filed 

-Format 

      Data level : Color = Blue,  Display Unit = Thousands, Value Decimals = 2, Text Size = 20 , Font Family = Arial Black 

     Category = 0ff  

      Title : On > Title Text= Entry Per Day, Word  Wrap = on , Background Color = Gray , Font = Sigoe (Bold) 

       Background : On> Background color= white , Transparency = 100 % 

      General :   X position =  0, Y position = 272 , Width=171, Height = 143

      Border  = ON 

      Shadow = On

     Tool tip = On

    Visual Heading = On

 


Create  YOY Entries KPI 

- Bring Card  from the visualization to the report pane > Diffs YOY  measure   as Filed 

-Format 

      Data level : Color = Blue,  Display Unit = Thousands, Value Decimals = 2, Text Size = 20 , Font Family = Arial Black 

      Category = Off 

      Title : On > Title Text= YOY , Word  Wrap = on , Background Color = Gray , Font = Sigoe (Bold) 

       Background : On> Background color= white , Transparency = 100 % 

      General :   X position =  0, Y position = 105, Width=171, Height = 165

      Border  = ON 

      Shadow = On

     Tool tip = On

    Visual Heading = On



Tips for Creating and formatting main KPI's , Watch

 https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PQAviqRSiWU
